parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoCl.1Hero. I sense some conflict in your mind.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Arianna… Were you meant to be found by Sister Judy?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArHaOp.There are no mistakes in God's will. You are the one who found the Oracle and you are the one I will guide.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I trust you, Arianna. I hope I’m doing the right thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArHaEx.I will always tell you the truth. I am incapable of anything else.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.It’s getting late… Is it too late to help Carol out with the tractor?");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.It’s all good now. I think we had a little mixup.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrSaEx^.You need to be careful, Sister Judy. There are lots of dangers out there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.I know, Father. I won’t do it again.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx^.Let’s hope that officers ward off those criminals.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’m going to do everything I can to end this soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.I… I should get back to my studies.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Are you going somewhere, 1Hero? It’s very late.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’m just stopping by to say hello.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Chloe left not long ago. Are you looking for her?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’m just stopping by to say hello.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.It’s good to see you again too, Sister Judy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Hopefully you don't have to save me from any spiders this time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOpNo3.Haha, I'm your knight in shining armor.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Would you like to stay a while? I sure do enjoy your company.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I’d like that, but I have somewhere to be. Maybe later this evening?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.I look forward to spending time with you this evening.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Are you going somewhere, 1Hero? It’s very late.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’m just stopping by to say hello.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.No sign of her yet. But I’ll keep looking.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.I’ve dealt with my share of difficult women in my life, but this Madalyn woman sounds like more than a handful.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.And what brings you here to the church on this lovely evening?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlDe.Of course… of course.  A young handsome man like you I’m sure puts Sister Judy’s mind at ease just before bedtime.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOp.You know me… I’m here to help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlOp.No worries, 1Hero. I’m sure you’re a better man than me at your age.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrCl.That’s not the kind of joke I’d expect to hear from an ordained priest of the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.I'm starting to wonder just how wild your past really was.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlDe.I've done things a man your age has probably never even heard of.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.She was so flexible, she could do any position in the Kama Sutra.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.Let me ask you, 1Hero. Have you ever done an upside down cowgirl?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlDe.How she never got pregnant, I’ll never know. It’s a miracle.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Well… Did you want a child of your own?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.I think I would have been a good father.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.You seem like you would have made for a cool dad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrDe.But then again, the Lord guided me here. Who am I to question His will?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrDe.Don't worry about Judy. I'll protect her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Oh, uhh... Yeah. Of course. Sister Judy needs our help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrSaDe.She has a complicated past with that woman, Madalyn. It's really done a number on her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Whatever's happening here in North Santiva, I'll get to the bottom of it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.I don’t mean to interrupt you two. But, 1Hero… Your clothes are dry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx.As much as I’d love to stay, I need to get going.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Wait. Father Solomon wanted me to make sure you don’t leave before he gets back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlDe.Are you going to try and stop me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Check your bedroom, Sister Judy. The leak is right above your room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.It may be several days before mass, but it takes time to prepare.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.I saw her go outside… I should get back to my studies.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Do you think you’ll stay in the cathedral tonight?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.I suppose it’s safe now… But I sure had fun with Chloe at her place…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I’m sure Father Solomon is lonely without you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.You’re right. But I do hope you’ll visit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.I don’t mean to keep you. I know you must get to the mansion with Father.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOpNo3.Haha. It’s only the restroom. How long could it take?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.This is kinda weird. But I guess it’s better safe than sorry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.Yes, Sister Judy. I will only be gone a moment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaEx.I gave her the relic… There’s still a chance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Did you tell her what to do with it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaDe.I… I told her what she needed to know to make a choice…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaEx.But, 1Hero… You don’t know what it’s like in Limbo… You don’t know what it’s like to die.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaEx.Erica is making a choice between eternal life and eternal damnation.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaEx.If she chooses damnation, she will be in the hands of Lilith.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I know you think I’m crazy, but I believe Lilith… I believe she loves Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnDe.A monster like her doesn’t know what love is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.There is good in her. I know it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Well… We’ll both find out soon enough.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaEx.I will keep an eye on Erica’s body from afar… If Lilith wishes to take it, I won’t stop her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Thanks for giving her a chance, Arianna.");
